title: TVS Motor enters Venezuelan market
description: TVS Motor Company is entering the Venezuelan market by launching 14 products, including motorcycles and three-wheelers, in collaboration with local distributor SERVISUMINISTROS JPG. The range of products includes premium motorcycles such as RR 310 and Apache RTR 200, as well as commuter bikes and sporty scooters. TVS Motor Company sees this move as a significant achievement in its global expansion strategy.
